name: New Day
description:
I made this bracelet after I woke up one morning & looked out of my window to see a gorgeous Spring morning with the sky changing from a dark blue to a bright fresh morning. 
All the felt beads are handmade by myself out of beautiful soft merino wool, the felt beads are all framed with silvercolored bead caps & seperated with natural wood beads all finished off with a Tibetan silver heart t-bar clasp & Tibetan silver leaf charm.
New Day measures 9" in length.

name: Aventurine Garden
description:
This one size fits all coil bracelet is made with a selection of different colors, shapes & textures. 
Aventurine Garden is made with a beautiful mixture of my own handmade merino felt beads, gorgeous large hand painted wood beads, little antique colored brass beads, wood beads & seeds. There is also a lot of gorgeous dark green Aventurine chips to add to the mix.
Aventurine is a calming gemstone that helps you fight your fears and rid your mind of anxiety.                                                 Aventurine helps reinforce decisive qualities  and gives you a felling of independence, also amplifies  leadership qualities.
